name: Bib Fortuna
Lore: 'Twi''lek who serves as Jabba''s major-domo. First to discover the profitability of ryll spice found on Ryloth.',
Text: 'While with Jabba, power +3 and, during your draw phase, may use 1 Force to count the number of cards in your Force Pile, place your Force Pile in your Used Pile, and then activate Force up to the counted number.',
